('29074','46','0','There... There\'s no more time for me. I\'m done for. Finish me off, $N. Do it or they\'ll kill us both. $N... Remember Gnomeregan! This world is worth saving.','12','0','100','0','0','0','special_surprise SAY_EXEC_TIME_5'),
